description.en: TenUp is a masternode based POS coin. TenUp believes that every individual is blessed with some great skill set and some of those have great passion and enthusiasm to transform their ideas to identities. To provide a push to such creative and intellectual minds, TenUp has come up with a completely unique and out-of-the box solution. A blockchain based venture capitalist platform to connect the ideas with the investors who are ready to put their trust in highly feasible proposals and providing the transparency and trust that is currently lacking especially when distances are involved.
